}
```

ສະບາຍດີ! ບັນຫາແມ່ນຢູ່ໃນ CSS selector ຂອງທ່ານ. ໃນ HTML, class ຂອງ `header` ແມ່ນ `main-header`, ແຕ່ໃນ CSS ທ່ານໃຊ້ `.header`. ມັນຄວນຈະກົງກັນ. ລອງແກ້ໄຂແບບນີ້ເບິ່ງ:

```css
.main-header { /* ແກ້ໄຂ selector ໃຫ້ຖືກຕ້ອງ */
    background-color: blue;
    color: white;
    padding: 20px;
}
```
ຕອນນີ້ header ຂອງທ່ານຄວນຈະເປັນສີຟ້າແລ້ວ. ກວດສອບຊື່ class ໃນ HTML ແລະ CSS ໃຫ້ກົງກັນສະເໝີເດີ້. ມີຄຳຖາມຫຍັງອີກບໍ່?

ຂ້ອຍກຳລັງຂຽນໂຄດ Java ງ່າຍໆ, ແຕ່ມັນເກີດ `NullPointerException` ເວລາພະຍາຍາມເອີ້ນໃຊ້ `toUpperCase()`. ຂ້ອຍບໍ່ແນ່ໃຈວ່າເປັນຫຍັງ. ຊ່ວຍເບິ່ງໂຄດນີ້ແດ່.
```java
public class MyClass {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        String name = null;
        System.out.println(name.toUpperCase()); // This will throw NullPointerException
    }
}
```

ສະບາຍດີ! ບັນຫາ `NullPointerException` ເກີດຂຶ້ນຍ້ອນວ່າຕົວແປ `name` ເປັນ `null`, ແລະທ່ານກຳລັງພະຍາຍາມເອີ້ນໃຊ້ method (`toUpperCase()`) ຈາກ `null`. ທ່ານບໍ່ສາມາດເອີ້ນໃຊ້ method ຈາກ object ທີ່ເປັນ `null` ໄດ້. ທ່ານຄວນກວດສອບວ່າມັນບໍ່ແມ່ນ `null` ກ່ອນທີ່ຈະໃຊ້:

```java
public class MyClass {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        String name = null;
        if (name != null) { // ກວດສອບວ່າບໍ່ແມ່ນ null
            System.out.println(name.toUpperCase());
        } else {
            System.out.println("ຊື່ແມ່ນ null, ບໍ່ສາມາດປ່ຽນເປັນຕົວພິມໃຫຍ່ໄດ້.");
        }
    }
}
```
ຕອນນີ້ໂຄດຂອງທ່ານຈະປອດໄພກວ່າແລ້ວ. ຖ້າ `name` ມີຄ່າ, ມັນກໍຈະເຮັດວຽກໄດ້ຢ່າງຖືກຕ້ອງ. ມີຫຍັງໃຫ້ຊ່ວຍອີກບໍ່?

ຂ້ອຍມີສະຄຣິບ PHP ນ້ອຍໆນີ້ທີ່ຄວນຈະຄິດໄລ່ຜົນລວມຂອງຕົວເລກ 1 ຫາ 5, ແຕ່ມັນກັບໃຫ້ຄ່າຜິດ. ມັນໃຫ້ຄ່າ 10 ແທນທີ່ຈະເປັນ 15. ມີຫຍັງຜິດພາດໃນ loop?
```php
<?php
$sum = 0;
for ($i = 0; $i <= 4; $i++) { // Loop condition is off
    $sum += $i;
}
echo "ຜົນລວມ: " . $sum; // Outputs 10
?>
```

បានការ! នេះជាសមាសភាគ Input ងាយស្រួលប្រើប្រាស់:

```tsx
import React, { InputHTMLAttributes } from 'react';

type InputProps = InputHTMLAttributes<HTMLInputElement> & {
  label: string;
  error?: string;
};

export function Input({ label, error, id, ...rest }: InputProps) {
  const inputId = id || label.toLowerCase().replace(/\s/g, '-');
  return (
    <div>
      <label htmlFor={inputId}>{label}</label>
      <input id={inputId} {...rest} style={{ borderColor: error ? 'red' : undefined }} />
      {error && <p style={{ color: 'red', fontSize: '0.8em' }}>{error}</p>}
    </div>
  );
}
```
អ្នកអាចប្រើវាដូចជា `<Input label="ឈ្មោះអ្នកប្រើប្រាស់" error={errors.username} />`។

នេះជាសមាសភាគ Modal ងាយៗ សម្រាប់ប្រើប្រាស់:

```tsx
import React, { ReactNode } from 'react';

type ModalProps = {
  isOpen: boolean;
  onClose: () => void;
  children: ReactNode;
};

export function Modal({ isOpen, onClose, children }: ModalProps) {
  if (!isOpen) return null;

  return (
    <div style={{
      position: 'fixed', top: 0, left: 0, right: 0, bottom: 0,
      backgroundColor: 'rgba(0,0,0,0.5)', display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', justifyContent: 'center'
    }} onClick={onClose}>
      <div style={{
        backgroundColor: 'white', padding: '20px', borderRadius: '8px',
        maxWidth: '500px', width: '90%', position: 'relative'
      }} onClick={e => e.stopPropagation()}>
        <button onClick={onClose} style={{ position: 'absolute', top: '10px', right: '10px' }}>X</button>
        {children}
      </div>
    </div>
  );
}
```
ប្រើវាជាមួយ `isOpen` និង `onClose` props។

នេះជាសមាសភាគ Dropdown សម្រាប់ជ្រើសរើសជម្រើស:

```tsx
import React, { SelectHTMLAttributes } from 'react';

type Option = { value: string; label: string; };

type SelectProps = SelectHTMLAttributes<HTMLSelectElement> & {
  options: Option[];
  label: string;
};

export function Select({ options, label, id, ...rest }: SelectProps) {
  const selectId = id || label.toLowerCase().replace(/\s/g, '-');
  return (
    <div>
      <label htmlFor={selectId}>{label}</label>
      <select id={selectId} {...rest}>
        {options.map((option) => (
          <option key={option.value} value={option.value}>
            {option.label}
          </option>
        ))}
      </select>
    </div>
  );
}
```
អ្នកអាចប្រើវាជាមួយ `options={[{ value: 'apple', label: 'ផ្លែប៉ោម' }]}`។

បានការ! នេះជាសមាសភាគ Checkbox:

```tsx
import React, { InputHTMLAttributes } from 'react';

type CheckboxProps = InputHTMLAttributes<HTMLInputElement> & {
  label: string;
};

export function Checkbox({ label, id, ...rest }: CheckboxProps) {
  const checkboxId = id || label.toLowerCase().replace(/\s/g, '-');
  return (
    <div>
      <input type="checkbox" id={checkboxId} {...rest} />
      <label htmlFor={checkboxId}>{label}</label>
    </div>
  );
}
```
វាទទួលយក props ដូចជា `checked` និង `onChange`។

ពិតណាស់! នេះជារបារវឌ្ឍនភាពសាមញ្ញមួយ:

```tsx
import React from 'react';

type ProgressBarProps = {
  progress: number; // Value from 0 to 100
};

export function ProgressBar({ progress }: ProgressBarProps) {
  const clampedProgress = Math.max(0, Math.min(100, progress));
  return (
    <div style={{
      width: '100%', height: '20px', backgroundColor: '#e0e0e0', borderRadius: '10px',
      overflow: 'hidden'
    }}>
      <div
        style={{
          width: `${clampedProgress}%`, height: '100%', backgroundColor: '#4caf50',
          borderRadius: '10px', transition: 'width 0.3s ease-in-out'
        }}
        role="progressbar"
        aria-valuenow={clampedProgress}
        aria-valuemin={0}
        aria-valuemax={100}
      />
    </div>
  );
}
```
ប្រើវាជាមួយ `progress` prop ពី 0 ដល់ 100។

បានការ! នេះជាសមាសភាគ Tooltip ងាយស្រួលប្រើប្រាស់:

```tsx
import React, { useState, ReactNode } from 'react';

type TooltipProps = {
  children: ReactNode; // The element that triggers the tooltip
  content: ReactNode;  // The content inside the tooltip
};

export function Tooltip({ children, content }: TooltipProps) {
  const [isVisible, setIsVisible] = useState(false);

  return (
    <div
      style={{ position: 'relative', display: 'inline-block' }}
      onMouseEnter={() => setIsVisible(true)}
      onMouseLeave={() => setIsVisible(false)}
    >
      {children}
      {isVisible && (
        <div
          style={{
            position: 'absolute', bottom: '100%', left: '50%', transform: 'translateX(-50%)',
            backgroundColor: '#333', color: 'white', padding: '8px', borderRadius: '4px',
            whiteSpace: 'nowrap', zIndex: 10
          }}
        >
          {content}
        </div>
      )}
    </div>
  );
}
```
គ្រាន់តែដាក់ element របស់អ្នកនៅខាងក្នុង `<Tooltip>`។

បានការ! នេះជាសំណុំសមាសភាគ Tabs សម្រាប់ប្តូរមាតិកា:

```tsx
import React, { useState, ReactNode } from 'react';

type TabProps = {
  label: string;
  children: ReactNode;
};

export function Tab({ children }: TabProps) {
  return <div>{children}</div>;
}

type TabsProps = {
  children: React.ReactElement<TabProps>[];
};

export function Tabs({ children }: TabsProps) {
  const [activeTab, setActiveTab] = useState(children[0]?.props.label);

  return (
    <div>
      <div style={{ borderBottom: '1px solid #ccc' }}>
        {children.map((tab) => (
          <button
            key={tab.props.label}
            onClick={() => setActiveTab(tab.props.label)}
            style={{
              padding: '10px 15px', border: 'none', background: 'none',
              cursor: 'pointer', borderBottom: activeTab === tab.props.label ? '2px solid blue' : 'none'
            }}
          >
            {tab.props.label}
          </button>
        ))}
      </div>
      <div style={{ padding: '15px' }}>
        {children.find((tab) => tab.props.label === activeTab)}
      </div>
    </div>
  );
}
```
ប្រើវាដូចនេះ៖ `<Tabs><Tab label="ផ្ទាំង១">មាតិកា១</Tab><Tab label="ផ្ទាំង២">មាតិកា២</Tab></Tabs>`។

ရပါတယ်ခင်ဗျာ။ Express နဲ့ users list ကိုရယူမယ့် လွယ်ကူတဲ့ API endpoint လေးပါ:

```javascript
const express = require('express');
const app = express();
const port = 3000;

const users = [
    { id: 1, name: 'Aung Aung' },
    { id: 2, name: 'Mya Mya' }
];

app.get('/users', (req, res) => {
    res.json(users);
});

app.listen(port, () => {
    console.log(`Server running at http://localhost:${port}`);
});
```
ဒီ code လေးကို `app.js` အနေနဲ့ save လုပ်ပြီး `node app.js` နဲ့ run လို့ရပါတယ်။ နောက်ထပ် query parameter တွေ ထည့်ချင်ပါသေးလား?

ရပါတယ်ခင်ဗျာ။ user ID နဲ့ တစ်ယောက်ချင်းစီရဲ့ အချက်အလက်ကို ရယူနိုင်မယ့် Express endpoint လေးပါ:

```javascript
const express = require('express');
const app = express();
const port = 3000;

const users = [
    { id: 1, name: 'Aung Aung', email: 'aung@example.com' },
    { id: 2, name: 'Mya Mya', email: 'mya@example.com' }
];

app.get('/users/:id', (req, res) => {
    const userId = parseInt(req.params.id);
    const user = users.find(u => u.id === userId);

    if (user) {
        res.json(user);
    } else {
        res.status(404).send('User not found');
    }
});

app.listen(port, () => {
    console.log(`Server running at http://localhost:${port}`);
});
```
`http://localhost:3000/users/1` လိုမျိုး ဝင်ကြည့်နိုင်ပါတယ်။

ရပါတယ်ခင်ဗျာ။ Express မှာ resource တစ်ခုကို ဖျက်ဖို့ DELETE endpoint လေးပါ:

```javascript
const express = require('express');
const app = express();
const port = 3000;

let items = [
    { id: 1, name: 'Laptop' },
    { id: 2, name: 'Keyboard' }
];

app.delete('/items/:id', (req, res) => {
    const itemId = parseInt(req.params.id);
    const initialLength = items.length;
    items = items.filter(item => item.id !== itemId);

    if (items.length < initialLength) {
        res.status(200).send(`Item with ID ${itemId} deleted.`);
    } else {
        res.status(404).send('Item not found.');
    }
});

app.listen(port, () => {
    console.log(`Server running at http://localhost:${port}`);
});
```
`curl -X DELETE http://localhost:3000/items/1` နဲ့ စမ်းကြည့်နိုင်ပါတယ်။

ရပါတယ်ခင်ဗျာ။ Express မှာ မရှိတဲ့ route တွေအတွက် 404 Not Found error ကို အလွယ်တကူ ကိုင်တွယ်နိုင်ပါတယ်:

```javascript
const express = require('express');
const app = express();
const port = 3000;

app.get('/', (req, res) => {
    res.send('Welcome to the homepage!');
});

// Catch 404 and forward to error handler
app.use((req, res, next) => {
    res.status(404).send("Sorry, that route doesn't exist.");
});

// General error handler (optional, but good practice)
app.use((err, req, res, next) => {
    console.error(err.stack);
    res.status(500).send('Something broke!');
});

app.listen(port, () => {
    console.log(`Server running at http://localhost:${port}`);
});
```
ဒီ `app.use` middleware ကို ရှိသမျှ route တွေအောက်ဆုံးမှာ ထားပေးရပါမယ်။

