ရပါတယ်ခင်ဗျာ။ Express မှာ `tasks` ကို ID နဲ့ ဖျက်ဖို့ `DELETE` endpoint လေးပါ:

```javascript
const express = require('express');
const app = express();
const port = 3000;

let tasks = [
  { id: 1, description: 'Learn Express', completed: false },
  { id: 2, description: 'Build an API', completed: true },
];

app.delete('/tasks/:id', (req, res) => {
  const taskId = parseInt(req.params.id);
  const initialLength = tasks.length;
  tasks = tasks.filter(t => t.id !== taskId);

  if (tasks.length < initialLength) {
    res.status(204).send(); // No Content
  } else {
    res.status(404).send('Task not found');
  }
});

app.listen(port, () => {
  console.log(`Server running at http://localhost:${port}`);
});
```
ဖျက်ပြီးရင် `204 No Content` status ကို ပြန်ပေးပါတယ်။

ရပါတယ်ခင်ဗျာ။ Express မှာ data မတွေ့ရင် 404 error ပြန်ပေးဖို့ လွယ်ကူတဲ့ နည်းလမ်းလေးပါ:

```javascript
const express = require('express');
const app = express();
const port = 3000;

const users = [
  { id: 1, name: 'Alice' },
  { id: 2, name: 'Bob' },
];

app.get('/users/:id', (req, res) => {
